{
  "stem": "14928.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 585.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the other, whatever, belongs to Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Russians are going to stay there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was a-- well, Dubienka actually was in one side of the Bug.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH] was on the other side of the Bug.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Bug is a big river-- not that big, but according to Dubienka, there were a little rivers.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So this was a big river.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the Bug was actually the border, where they made the division of Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we didn't know where the division is going to be.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So since the Russians came to Dubienka also, we thought they going to stay there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But it didn't take long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And they had to go back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So when they had to go back, and we knew that the Germans are coming in to Dubienka, they-- I, for first, didn't want to stay there.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because I knew a lot about-- you know, I-- so I didn't want to stay there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And then my sisters-- she wasn't married yet, also, the middle sister-- she, too, didn't want to stay there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So we both left.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We left--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My parents still stayed there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They figured that they could always leave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they had my sister-- older sister had already two children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they stayed with them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We lived-- we lived together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we left.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everything was so fast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Here it was maybe one week.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my parents, and my sister, and my brother-in-law took the children and decided to leave also.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Because my father was a very-- very well read.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he knew everything what's-- what is going on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But it's hard to leave a home and just go, not knowing where.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So-- but when my older sister decided that they want to leave-- her husband, the children-- so they decided they'll go with them.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
